  <source>GlaxoSmithKline</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to determine the incidence of intussusceptions (IS) (including suspected
      cases of intussusception) after vaccination with Oral Rotarix® under clinical practice, in
      Japan.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is non-interventional study conducted in one group received Oral Rotarix®.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
